# Tick-Tock work folder — what to keep vs treat as transient.
#
# KEEP (committed, the durable proof + audit trail):
#   hypotheses/*.md   — the chosen recipe + candidates + summaries
#   seeds/*.txt       — the exact --seed-gene args a tock consumed
#   analysis/*.md     — the phenotype report that drove each hypothesis
#   peek_ledger.jsonl — every held-out peek (erosion audit trail)
#   loop_state.json   — the loop position (so any fresh Claude reconstructs it)
#
# IGNORE (transient handshake state / bulky data, recreated on demand):
markers/
analysis/*.csv
